ZH: 我们应该享有自由、平等的权利。
EN: We should enjoy the rights of freedom and equality.

ZH: 他是这家公司的创始人，享有很高的声誉。
EN: He is the founder of this company and enjoys a high reputation.

ZH: 学生们应该享有优质的教育资源。
EN: Students should enjoy high-quality educational resources.

ZH: 她已经享有了退休的权益。
EN: She has already enjoyed the benefits of retirement.

ZH: 这个城市的居民享有免费的医疗保险。
EN: The residents of this city enjoy free medical insurance.

ZH: 现代女性应该享有同男性平等的权力。
EN: Modern women should enjoy equal rights as men.

ZH: 作为公民，我们都享有言论自由的权利。
EN: As citizens, we all enjoy the right to freedom of speech.

ZH: 版权法给予作家享有作品的独家权益。
EN: Copyright law grants authors exclusive rights to their works.

ZH: 每个人都应该享有平等的机会去追求自己的梦想。
EN: Everyone should have equal opportunities to pursue their dreams.

ZH: 这种品牌在市场上享有很高的知名度。
EN: This brand enjoys a high level of popularity in the market.

ZH: 这个国家的公民享有选举的权利。
EN: The citizens of this country enjoy the right to vote.

ZH: 孩子们应该享有安全与健康的成长环境。
EN: Children should enjoy a safe and healthy environment to grow up in.

ZH: 在这个岗位上他享有很高的权威。
EN: He enjoys a high level of authority in this position.

ZH: 公司的员工享有年度假期。
EN: The company's employees enjoy annual vacations.

ZH: 美国宪法赋予人们享有追求幸福的权利。
EN: The U.S. Constitution grants people the right to pursue happiness.

ZH: 她是一位享有广泛赞誉的作家。
EN: She is a widely acclaimed writer.

ZH: 这个酒店享有迷人的海滩景色。
EN: This hotel enjoys a charming beach view.

ZH: 她过着优越的生活，享有各种奢侈品。
EN: She lives a luxurious life and enjoys various luxuries.

ZH: 这部电影在影评界享有好评。
EN: This movie is well-received in the film review industry.

ZH: 她是一位享有国际声誉的音乐家。
EN: She is a musician who enjoys international fame.
